{
  "id": "68d7cdc29866af20ca21d806",
  "title": "k-ベクトルの内積の成分表示",
  "created": 1758973389,
  "updated": 1758980051,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "68d7cdc29866af20ca21d806",
      "text": "k-ベクトルの内積の成分表示",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758973389,
      "updated": 1758973389
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7cdcc000000000097d7f8",
      "text": "from [多様体まで丁寧に歩く解析学問題集]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758973389,
      "updated": 1758973398
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7cdce000000000097d7f9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758973391,
      "updated": 1758973391
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7cdd7000000000097d7fa",
      "text": "[[問題]]: (k-ベクトルの内積): エルミート行列[$ M=M^\\dag\\in K^n]を用いて内積を[$ \\lang\\bm x,\\bm y\\rang=\\bm x^\\dag M\\bm y]で定めるとき、k-ベクトル[$ \\bm a,\\bm b\\in\\wedge^k(K^n)]の内積を成分[$ a_{i,j},b_{i,j,},m_{i,j}]を用いて表せ。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758973400,
      "updated": 1758973403
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7cdd8000000000097d7fb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758973400,
      "updated": 1758973400
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7de93000000000097d80c",
      "text": "行列[$ A]の行列式の成分表示は",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758977683,
      "updated": 1758977696
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7dea1000000000097d80d",
      "text": "\t[$ \\det(A)=\\sum_{\\sigma\\in\\Lambda((1,\\cdots,n))}{\\rm sgn}(\\sigma)\\prod_{i=1}^na_{i,\\sigma(i)}]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758977697,
      "updated": 1758978418
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7cddc000000000097d7fc",
      "text": "行列[$ A]の行列式を余因子(cofactor)[$ c_{i,j}(A)]で表すと",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758973405,
      "updated": 1758976126
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7cfb6000000000097d801",
      "text": "\t[$ \\det(A)=\\sum_{j=1}^n a_{i,j}c_{i,j}(A)=\\bm a_i^\\top\\bm c_i(A)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758973879,
      "updated": 1758977370
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7e1d0000000000097d810",
      "text": "ズレた余因子の積和は、[$ a_{i,j}:=a_{k,j}]となっている行列の行列式[$ \\det(A_{i:=k})]を求めれば良い。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758978513,
      "updated": 1758979337
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7e431000000000097d813",
      "text": "\t[$ a_{i,j}=a_{k,j}]なので[$ A_k]を構成するベクトルは一次従属",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758979122,
      "updated": 1758979162
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7e373000000000097d812",
      "text": " [$ \\therefore\\sum_{j=1}^na_{i,j}c_{k,j}(A)=\\det(A_{i:=k})=0]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758978932,
      "updated": 1758979385
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7d1c7000000000097d803",
      "text": "余因子行列は、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758974408,
      "updated": 1758974419
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7d1d4000000000097d804",
      "text": "\t[$ C=\\left\\lbrack c_{i,j}(A)\\right\\rbrack_{i,j}]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758974420,
      "updated": 1758974492
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7cea0000000000097d7ff",
      "text": "古典随伴行列(adjungate matrix)と行列の積は",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758973601,
      "updated": 1758974014
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7d03d000000000097d802",
      "text": "\t[$ \\tilde AA=C(A)^\\top A=\\left\\lbrack \\sum_{j=1}^na_{i,j}c_{k,j}(A)\\right\\rbrack_{i,k}=\\det(A)I]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758974014,
      "updated": 1758976789
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7daf3000000000097d809",
      "text": " [$ \\therefore A^{-1}=\\frac{\\tilde A}{\\det(A)}]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758976755,
      "updated": 1758977655
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7cddc000000000097d7fd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758973405,
      "updated": 1758973405
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7e568000000000097d815",
      "text": "k-ベクトルの内積は",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758979433,
      "updated": 1758979449
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7e579000000000097d816",
      "text": "\t[$ \\lang\\bm a,\\bm b\\rang=\\det(\\lbrack\\lang\\bm a_i,\\bm b_j\\rang\\rbrack_{i,j})]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758979451,
      "updated": 1758979507
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7e5bf000000000097d817",
      "text": "\t[$ =\\det(\\lbrack\\bm a_i^\\dag M\\bm b_j\\rbrack_{i,j})]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758979519,
      "updated": 1758979567
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7e546000000000097d814",
      "text": "\t[$ =\\det\\left(\\left\\lbrack\\sum_{(\\kappa,\\lambda)=(1,1)}^{(n,n)}\\overline{a_{i,\\kappa}} m_{\\kappa,\\lambda}b_{\\lambda,j}\\right\\rbrack_{i,j}\\right)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758979398,
      "updated": 1758979861
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7e738000000000097d819",
      "text": "\t[$ =\\sum_{\\sigma\\in\\Lambda((1,\\cdots,n))}{\\rm sgn}(\\sigma)\\prod_{i=1}^n\\left(\\sum_{(\\kappa,\\lambda)=(1,1)}^{(n,n)}\\overline{a_{i,\\kappa}} m_{\\kappa,\\lambda}b_{\\lambda,\\sigma(i)}\\right)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758979897,
      "updated": 1758980051
    },
    {
      "id": "68d7e5f5000000000097d818",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1758979574,
      "updated": 1758979574
    }
  ]
}